{
  "stem": "26609.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They begin-- it must be-- it must have been middle-- if I do remember exactly, I don't know exactly-- it must have been '41.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The name?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't-- I didn't-- I never knew him even.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have never-- my mother knew him, but I didn't know him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know if they-- what they did to him, because the people who hid Jews, they killed them too.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I asked my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said she doesn't know, she-- because he took her away from there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a part of Grodek where, even before the war, it was like a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was not a ghetto, but like.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There lived only Jews there, in Grodek.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's where they took my mother and father, before they killed them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And how they killed them, my parents, [SIGHS] that, I found out later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- I don't know exactly, but I found it out later from a person who survived there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But not in-- no one survived there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he was hidden outside, he and his brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They both were hidden outside by peasants.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he survived, his brother did not.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His brother went out too early after the war and was killed by the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know who these [NON-ENGLISH] were-- Poles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And his brother survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Otherwise, I wouldn't know how my parents died, but-- or were murdered.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I have been in Israel-- I don't know if I mentioned to you-- a few years, since '76 to '84.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there, I met that person, who survived, whose brother was killed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was from Grodek.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he told me how these people-- including my parents, of course-- how they were murdered.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They took them all together, from that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't know how many could be there-- about a few hundred.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
